Watchword:  I have a few of these now trying to eventually get them all one by one as I am buying them used. I now own Revelation, Galations and James which I prefer as the best. There is more of the shadowy movements in the backgrownd of James as they should be shadowy so they don't draw away from the message. I prefer James as the best one so far there is as I said is more in the background so my favorite so far.
